?", "- Det handler om mot. Politikerne vil jo bli gjenvalgt, og da er det ikke enkelt \u00e5 ta disse valgene. Men skal man gj\u00f8re superbussen super m\u00e5 man ta t\u00f8ffe valg.", "F\u00f8lg Adresseavisen p\u00e5 Facebook , Instagram og Twitter ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "91a3285967413a1b30612b9048871d414301bd9f812ec759721662a4b4d2f84f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-01T05:28:12.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Professor Tor Medalen tror ikke p\u00e5 bilfri midtby. Men Elgeseter bru mener han ikke har plass til privatbiler om f\u00e5 \u00e5r."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article14327091.ece/a5jumn/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_Biltrafikk02.jpg_1_1_84A9FNR.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/23ffac87543ff01d4dc12f2056ccce23f8a056d6.jpg?5986290b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["NTNU-professor mener Elgeseter bru m\u00e5 bli bilfri -adressa.no", "Korttidsparkering", "Tiltak", "Ingen biler over Elgeseter bru", "T\u00f8ffe valg"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "23ffac87543ff01d4dc12f2056ccce23f8a056d6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Byutvikling", "superbuss"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Byutvikling,superbuss"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["superbuss", "valg", "bru", "midtby", "plass", "t\u00f8ffe valg", "bilfri", "buss"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nordre", "midtbyen", "adresseavisen", "elgeseter", "byscenen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "kolkata", "groningen", "freiburg", "g\u00f6teborg", "calcutta", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pa